RATIONALE: EN 50716:2023, Clause 5.1 – Organisation.

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: SP-021
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Independence of the verifier
STATEMENT: >>>
The Software Verifier shall be independent of the development activities
at the level required by the target SIL per EN 50716:2023, Clause 5.1:

  SIL 1: The verifier shall be a different person from the author of the
          artefact under review; independence within the same team is acceptable.

  SIL 2: The verifier shall belong to a different group or team within the
          same organisation.

  SIL 3: The verifier shall be from an independent organisational unit with
          no line-management authority over the development team.

  SIL 4: The verifier shall be from a fully independent organisation.

The designated Software Verifier for this project is: <Name / Organisation>.
Independence evidence: <describe reporting lines and contractual separation>
<<<
