TITLE: Planning verification records
STATEMENT: >>>
The outcome of the planning verification shall be recorded and shall include:

  - Date and revision of each planning document reviewed.
  - Name and role of the verifier.
  - List of findings and their severity.
  - Action items raised, with reference to the action item register.
  - Overall verdict: Approved / Approved with conditions / Not approved.

Planning verification shall be conducted by the Software Verifier (SP-021).
Development activities for which a plan is required shall not commence until
the corresponding plan has been approved.

