[[SECTION]]
TITLE: Software Configuration Management Plan (SCMP)

[TEXT]
STATEMENT: >>>
This section constitutes the Software Configuration Management Plan as required
by EN 50716:2023, Clause 5.3. The SCMP defines the strategy for identifying,
controlling, recording, and auditing software configuration items throughout
the lifecycle, and addresses change and modification control per Clause 6.6.
<<<

